WEBVTT

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:28.920
Wei.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.200
What should we do now?

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:53.400
Now Su Changming has also gotten involved.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:56.200
Things are getting more and more complicated.

00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:57.160
I told you long ago

00:00:57.160 --> 00:00:58.760
that woman can't be trusted.

00:00:59.280 --> 00:00:59.920
However,

00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:02.040
he didn't tell Chen Jingbian

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:03.480
about your deception.

00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:05.880
That means there's still room to maneuver.

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:09.810
I'll figure something out.

00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:11.610
What are you going to do?

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:13.050
Don't do anything rash.

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:14.820
The simplest solution now

00:01:14.880 --> 00:01:17.880
is to hand over both the person and the sword to Su Changming.

00:01:17.880 --> 00:01:19.520
We might even be able to use him

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:21.120
to get the Night Firefly Map.

00:01:22.160 --> 00:01:22.620
Li Ling.

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:23.200
Hey.

00:01:23.560 --> 00:01:25.160
Are you even listening to me?

00:01:27.880 --> 00:01:30.240
The Tang army is about to enter Chang'an City!

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:32.600
The Tang army is entering Chang'an City!

00:01:33.360 --> 00:01:35.620
The Tang army is entering Chang'an City!

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:38.140
The Tang army is entering Chang'an City!

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:39.240
Don't run so fast!

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:41.280
Sister! Yu!

00:01:41.800 --> 00:01:43.680
Sister, someone's coming!

00:01:44.360 --> 00:01:45.320
Yezi, come here.

00:01:48.360 --> 00:01:49.280
Don't be afraid.

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.080
He's my friend

00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:51.770
and he's with the Tang army.

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:53.880
Why are you standing there?

00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:55.759
Come in quickly. We're having saozi noodles today.

00:01:55.759 --> 00:01:57.160
No help, no food for you.

00:01:58.600 --> 00:01:59.200
All right.

00:02:06.280 --> 00:02:07.640
Come on, try my cooking.

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:11.920
How is it? Tasty?

00:02:12.320 --> 00:02:13.480
Delicious!

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:16.920
Eat slowly.

00:02:25.160 --> 00:02:25.890
It's so good!

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:26.880
I love

00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:28.540
these saozi noodles you make.

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:29.970
If you like them,

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:31.880
I'll make them for you every day.

00:02:31.880 --> 00:02:32.720
Nonsense!

00:02:33.079 --> 00:02:35.079
You're my deputy commander now,

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:36.280
not some cook.

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:38.900
Use that time to train soldiers instead.

00:02:39.600 --> 00:02:40.130
Yes, sir.

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:53.250
You haven't taken a wife yet, have you?

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:55.280
Not yet.

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:58.040
I've thought of a perfect solution.

00:02:58.520 --> 00:03:00.840
I have a daughter named Yinniang.

00:03:01.160 --> 00:03:03.240
Though she has a bit of a temper,

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:06.080
she's quite beautiful,

00:03:06.320 --> 00:03:07.450
and very clever too.

00:03:07.480 --> 00:03:09.680
Whoever marries her will be a lucky man.

00:03:10.160 --> 00:03:12.360
If you have what it takes to win her over,

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:15.000
then I could enjoy these noodles every day.

00:03:16.320 --> 00:03:17.180
Think about it.

00:03:17.480 --> 00:03:18.079
All right.

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:23.770
I suddenly feel these noodles smell even better now.

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:27.360
This time when you went back,

00:03:27.360 --> 00:03:30.400
it's fortunate that Chen Jingbian didn't suspect you.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.880
By the way, what about me?

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:33.500
What does he plan to do?

00:03:37.040 --> 00:03:38.700
Has he sent anyone to find you?

00:03:39.200 --> 00:03:40.200
Even if he doesn't look for me,

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:41.600
I'll find a way to go back.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:44.370
After all, he can't stop taking his medicine.

00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:46.760
By the way,

00:03:47.240 --> 00:03:49.970
did you notice the color at the bottom of his eyes?

00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:52.120
The color of his eyes?

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:54.240
I didn't notice that.

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:54.760
Why?

00:03:55.720 --> 00:03:57.400
It seems it's not time yet,

00:03:57.760 --> 00:04:01.220
otherwise the whites of his eyes should be noticeably yellow.

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:03.320
I didn't tell you before,

00:04:03.760 --> 00:04:05.420
I tampered with his medicine.

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:08.840
I've been controlling the dosage to avoid detection.

00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:10.140
You mean...

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:12.520
I was worried that even if we got the Firefly Map,

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:14.000
it would be hard to tell if it's real.

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:16.529
So you're controlling him with the medicine.

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:19.440
According to my calculations,

00:04:19.440 --> 00:04:21.040
it should be almost time now.

00:04:21.399 --> 00:04:21.920
I see.

00:04:23.720 --> 00:04:25.320
You've planned everything.

00:04:36.200 --> 00:04:36.800
Thank you.

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:37.880
Yin Niang.

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:58.040
Young Master.

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:00.040
That Li Ling,

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:03.120
he won't be causing trouble behind our backs, will he?

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:05.320
It's too late for him to do anything now.

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:07.360
They're already like meat

00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:10.560
on a chopping board, ready to be sliced.

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:15.360
Young Master, a letter has arrived.

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:24.020
You see?

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:27.220
They still have to come begging to me.

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:31.640
Miss Yu.

00:05:32.320 --> 00:05:34.450
Here's the medicine prepared for you.

00:05:36.760 --> 00:05:37.490
Please wait.

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:42.920
When we rescued Qi the other day,

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:45.260
I spoke inappropriately.

00:05:46.200 --> 00:05:48.520
Please don't take it to heart, Miss Yu.

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:51.480
You're too kind, Mr. Zhuang.

00:05:51.960 --> 00:05:52.360
Wait.

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:54.920
Is there something else?

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:56.360
Li Ling.

00:05:59.200 --> 00:06:00.640
Has he told you anything?

00:06:01.320 --> 00:06:02.240
Told me what?

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:06.880
I knew it.

00:06:07.720 --> 00:06:08.920
It would be like this.

00:06:09.440 --> 00:06:10.100
Mr. Zhuang,

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.760
has something happened?

00:06:14.320 --> 00:06:16.720
Li Ling is just like that.

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:18.890
No matter what happens,

00:06:19.240 --> 00:06:20.640
he always bears it alone.

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:23.320
Chen Jingbian was the one who summoned Su Changming.

00:06:23.320 --> 00:06:24.080
Su Changming

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:26.960
is just a profit-seeking opportunist.

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:29.320
To obtain the Night Firefly Scroll,

00:06:29.440 --> 00:06:32.240
he has agreed to help Chen Jingbian hold Chang'an.

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:33.340
When that happens,

00:06:33.600 --> 00:06:35.860
there will surely be another bloodbath.

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:37.120
The Tang soldiers

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:40.650
and countless civilians in the city will suffer and die.

00:06:44.680 --> 00:06:45.340
Miss Nongyu

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:45.820
what are

00:06:46.120 --> 00:06:47.040
you doing?

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:49.640
As a secret agent of the imperial court,

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:51.840
I've spent half my life undercover.

00:06:52.159 --> 00:06:53.680
Now when our nation is in peril,

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:55.880
I've been given this critical mission.

00:06:56.200 --> 00:06:58.440
I've weathered many storms before

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:00.520
and survived them all on my own.

00:07:00.520 --> 00:07:01.520
But this time,

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:04.520
this crucial mission to recapture Chang'an...

00:07:04.520 --> 00:07:04.800
I...

00:07:05.200 --> 00:07:05.480
I...

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:07.780
I truly don't know what to do anymore.

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:11.520
Master Zhuang, please get up first.

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:16.200
Since Chang'an fell,

00:07:17.320 --> 00:07:19.180
our fellow undercover agents...

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:20.320
Some died,

00:07:20.400 --> 00:07:21.460
some were injured.

00:07:21.640 --> 00:07:23.080
Now only Li Ling and I remain,

00:07:23.080 --> 00:07:24.680
still struggling to hold on.

00:07:25.760 --> 00:07:28.220
Whether we can successfully retake the city

00:07:28.320 --> 00:07:30.640
depends entirely on intelligence transmission.

00:07:30.640 --> 00:07:31.370
Miss Nongyu.

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:33.560
We cannot allow Chen Jingbian

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:35.960
to cause more trouble with the Firefly Map.

00:07:36.760 --> 00:07:37.620
Master Zhuang,

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:40.090
please stand up when you speak.

00:07:42.640 --> 00:07:43.120
Miss Yu.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:47.460
About your background...

00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:50.130
Li Ling has already told me.

00:07:51.840 --> 00:07:54.040
I know you're General Feng's daughter.

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:56.320
General Feng spent his entire life in military service,

00:07:56.320 --> 00:07:57.960
all so that the people of the Tang Dynasty

00:07:57.960 --> 00:07:59.240
could live in peace.

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:00.640
As his daughter,

00:08:01.960 --> 00:08:02.640
you must

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:05.560
also understand what's right and just.

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:09.400
I know I shouldn't say these things,

00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:12.200
but for the sake of our Tang Dynasty,

00:08:12.320 --> 00:08:13.320
for all its people,

00:08:13.320 --> 00:08:14.120
for Li Ling...

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:17.200
I beg you, Miss Feng,

00:08:17.920 --> 00:08:19.320
to distract Su Changming

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:21.480
and retrieve the Night Firefly Map.

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:31.240
Li Ling.

00:08:31.600 --> 00:08:33.400
Where are my sword and the woman?

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:01.330
After all this talk,

00:09:01.400 --> 00:09:03.120
this is your real purpose.

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:05.640
You want me to distract Su Changming

00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:07.120
in exchange for the Firefly Map.

00:09:07.120 --> 00:09:09.250
You just want me to throw myself at him.

00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:11.290
Miss Nongyu,

00:09:11.760 --> 00:09:14.240
you're the only one who can do it now.

00:09:23.760 --> 00:09:26.820
Young Master, you're back. Someone is waiting for you.

00:09:30.080 --> 00:09:31.720
I heard that only if both I and the sword belong to you,

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:33.840
will you be willing to help the Tang Dynasty.

00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:35.100
Can you keep your word?

00:09:40.680 --> 00:09:41.840
I'm just a bandit.

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:43.200
I do terrible things

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:44.460
and break my promises.

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.520
Do you think I keep my word?

00:09:48.520 --> 00:09:49.580
Since you're here,

00:09:49.760 --> 00:09:51.490
you might as well sleep with me.

00:09:53.880 --> 00:09:55.320
Show me all those skills

00:09:55.560 --> 00:09:57.020
you used to please Li Ling.

00:09:58.480 --> 00:09:59.240
Hit me.

00:10:00.840 --> 00:10:02.000
Go ahead, hit me.

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:15.520
Last time I treated you this way,

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:19.720
you were completely unwilling.

00:10:20.440 --> 00:10:21.700
Why is it that this time

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:23.530
you're playing hard to get?

00:10:28.440 --> 00:10:30.240
Because you've already applied

00:10:30.520 --> 00:10:31.720
poison to your lips.

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:52.680
Try again.

00:10:56.240 --> 00:10:58.240
I won't fight anymore. I surrender.

00:10:59.320 --> 00:11:00.320
No more fighting?

00:11:02.800 --> 00:11:04.060
Then accept your loss.

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:05.780
Since you've lost,

00:11:06.160 --> 00:11:07.420
you should act like it.

00:11:07.800 --> 00:11:08.760
Where are my sword and woman?

00:11:08.760 --> 00:11:10.840
You will never get the person or the sword.

00:11:10.840 --> 00:11:11.240
You...

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:14.240
If I can't even protect

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:17.300
the person I love and my benefactor's relic,

00:11:17.600 --> 00:11:19.400
then I'm worse than a scoundrel.

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:20.800
Su Changming,

00:11:21.160 --> 00:11:22.890
don't you understand even now?

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:25.520
Even if you get the person and the sword,

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:27.240
you still won't be the winner.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:27.970
Ridiculous.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:30.440
I, Su Changming, have never lost.

00:11:31.120 --> 00:11:32.720
Deep down, you know very well

00:11:33.560 --> 00:11:35.820
that even if you keep Nongyu by your side,

00:11:35.960 --> 00:11:37.620
you will never truly have her.

00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:38.700
Because...

00:11:39.000 --> 00:11:40.660
She doesn't belong to anyone.

00:11:40.920 --> 00:11:42.520
She only belongs to herself.

00:11:43.400 --> 00:11:44.000
Actually,

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:46.130
what you really want

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:48.200
is my life, isn't it?

00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:50.160
Fine then.

00:11:50.880 --> 00:11:51.940
I'll give it to you.

00:11:53.960 --> 00:11:54.890
What do you mean?

00:11:57.480 --> 00:11:58.680
I'll give you my life,

00:11:59.920 --> 00:12:01.320
but I have one condition.

00:12:02.040 --> 00:12:03.640
You and the Guantian Society

00:12:03.800 --> 00:12:05.130
must join the Tang army.

00:12:05.960 --> 00:12:06.480
Li Ling,

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:09.060
have you gone mad out of desperation?

00:12:09.240 --> 00:12:11.440
I lead my brothers to enjoy the good life

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:12.530
and live freely.

00:12:12.840 --> 00:12:14.280
Why would I be foolish enough

00:12:14.280 --> 00:12:15.480
to join the Tang army?

00:12:16.280 --> 00:12:17.080
For honor.

00:12:17.520 --> 00:12:18.240
Honor?

00:12:18.720 --> 00:12:21.640
You killed your commander and betrayed your master for glory.

00:12:21.640 --> 00:12:23.840
What right do you have to talk about honor?

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:24.840
What I'm doing now

00:12:25.760 --> 00:12:26.840
is the same as what Feng Jianye did

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:28.360
when he willingly offered his own head

00:12:28.360 --> 00:12:29.080
years ago.

00:12:29.720 --> 00:12:31.250
Stop glorifying yourself.

00:12:31.560 --> 00:12:32.960
After Tongguan fell,

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:34.940
the Emperor fled west,

00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:36.290
Chang'an was captured,

00:12:36.360 --> 00:12:38.090
and the Great Tang was in peril.

00:12:38.400 --> 00:12:39.160
General Feng

00:12:39.160 --> 00:12:41.240
wanted me to go undercover beside Chen Jingbian

00:12:41.240 --> 00:12:42.880
to obtain the Night Firefly Map.

00:12:42.880 --> 00:12:44.340
That's why he chose to die,

00:12:44.400 --> 00:12:46.260
sacrificing himself willingly.

00:12:46.520 --> 00:12:48.180
All these lies you're telling

00:12:48.400 --> 00:12:50.280
are just to absolve yourself of guilt.

00:12:50.280 --> 00:12:53.010
You can cut off my head, Li Ling's head, right now.

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.400
What are you waiting for?

